				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${Q}_{0}={Q}_{\min }+\frac{N}{35}\left({Q}_{\max }-{Q}_{\min }\right),$$\end{document}where N/35 is the ratio of the ambient nitrogen concentration at the time of seeding to the a representative N concentration below the nutricline (35 μM).
